Save Manapouri campaign
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an extensive nationwide campaign to prevent high level raising of Lake Manapouri for hydroelectricity generation.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:Environment
Region:[none]
